<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>If you have a class implementing an Aware interface, the only way to inject setters it defines is via DI preferences. You cannot specify alternates on a per class basis, such as the following:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$di-&gt;configure(new Configuration(array(
    'instance' =&gt; array(
        'Foo\Bar\Baz' =&gt; array(
            'foo' =&gt; 'Foo\Bar\Foo', // where the "foo" parameter is defined in an "Aware" interface
        ),
    ),
));
</code></pre>

